{"_id":"04o2fJQ4NeD0da1S","name":"Escaping Fate","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Every time you use an omen there is a 50% chance it is not spent.</p>","rollFormula":"d100","rollLabel":"Escape"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/gutterborn_scum.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"DgwcKHJBg5aqOP8T","name":"Armored Caster","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>May use powers while wearing medium armor.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/heretical_priest.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"GBFi2f3pYOtSNxV8","name":"Clumsy","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Normal Agility tests are DR14 instead of DR12, excluding defence.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/fanged_deserter.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"HyTPCkj2SueZA19g","name":"Filthy Fingersmith","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Your snaky little digits get into pockets and pick locks with a DR8 Agility test. You also begin with lockpicks!</p>","rollFormula":"1d20+@abilities.agility.value","rollLabel":"Pick"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/gutterborn_scum.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"M2F0GV9wnYBbbBTy","name":"Dodging Death","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>You are so unpleasant, irrelevant, disgusting and vile even Death would rather avoid you if it can. On death, if there is even the slightest possibility that you survived, there is a 50% chance that you did. If successful, after 10 rounds you pop back up with d4 HP and an unlikely explanation of your escape.</p>","rollFormula":"1d100","rollLabel":"Dodge"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/gutterborn_scum.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"NAmpVMmTiocYzaP2","name":"Master of Fate","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>What use are maps when the substance of causality itself is open to you? You know the right way with a DR8 Presence test.</p>","rollFormula":"1d20+@abilities.presence.value","rollLabel":"Know"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Pz8AXBNDpdGu5yMF","name":"Create Decoctions","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>You carry a portable laboratory and continually search for frequently expended ingredients. Daily you have the materials to create two randomly determined decoctions and can brew a total of d4 doses. If unused they lose vitality after 24 hours.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Red Poison</li>\n<li>Ezumiels Vapor</li>\n<li>Southern Frog Stew</li>\n<li>Elixir Vitalis</li>\n<li>Spider-Owl Soup</li>\n<li>Fernor's Philtre</li>\n<li>Hyphos Enervating Snuff</li>\n<li>Black Poison</li>\n</ol>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/occult_herbmaster.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"QFc99iAdYIKGsKX0","name":"Excretal Stealth","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>You have an astounding, almost preternatural ability to hide in muck, debris and filth. When hidden in these conditions a DR16 Presence test is required to notice you.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/gutterborn_scum.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"dFRoRZAr5LfqPAZB","name":"Initiate of the Invisible College","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Once per day you may summon D2 scrolls, whose power can be used only once. Roll a d4, on a 1&ndash;2 the scrolls are sacred, on a 3&ndash;4, unclean. If the scrolls are not used before sunrise they turn to ash.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nPUdUtsauKG42pBh","name":"Abominable Gob Lobber","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Your phlegm is viscous, lumpy, vile and ballistically accurate at short range. You can spit d2 times during a fight. Roll a DR8 Presence test for accuracy. Targets are blinded, retching and vomiting for d4 rounds. Anyone witnessing this&mdash;friend and foe&mdash;must make a Toughness test to not also vomit. PCs test DR10 and enemies DR12.</p>","rollFormula":"1d20+@abilities.presence.value","rollLabel":"Spit"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/gutterborn_scum.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"rQuoRtKR0VzwrmWw","name":"Speaker of Truths","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Twice per day use your wisdom, knowledge, advice and inner calm to bring clarity to a creature of your choice. The DR of the next test they undertake is lowered by 4.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"sHyrxqcJLCOm0LZg","name":"Bard of the Undying","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>You learnt your melodies in the Otherworld. The music of your Harp gives +D4 on reaction rolls.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/esoteric_hermit.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"wLyqytHZXXCrOuti","name":"Illiterate","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Illiterate; you are incapable of understanding scrolls. If you begin with one then reroll, eat it or use it as toilet paper.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/fanged_deserter.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"yd5OWDavGEHmRZWl","name":"Painfully Average","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>Painfully average, you adjust no abilities.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>It's not much of a feat, but hey.</p>","rollFormula":"","rollLabel":""},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/wretched_royalty.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"z2OHdCp6cBYXAYUZ","name":"Coward's Jab","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":"<p>When attacking by surprise test Agility DR10. On a success you automatically hit once with a light one-handed weapon, dealing normal damage +3.</p>","rollFormula":"1d20+@abilities.agility.value","rollLabel":"Jab","price":null,"carryWeight":null,"containerSpace":null},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/gutterborn_scum.png","effects":[]}
